data.description: Here is a must see home. This 3 Bed 2.5 Bath home is sitting on one of the cutest little streets on the west side of Indianapolis. This home features a large living room, with plenty of room for entertaining, and built in surround sound. Get away upstairs to the large bonus room great for kids or adults to have a place to relax, play games or watch TV. Sit outside on your private patio and relax near your gold fish pond. Master Bedroom has its own on-suit bathroom with dual sinks a separate shower and tub, and its own walk in closet. New Roof (2 years old), Hot Water Heater (a year old), Dishwasher (a year old), Water Softener is paid for (2 years old), also new Master Bath tile, and updated light fixtures in common areas. Easy access to US 65 that will have to downtown Indy in less that 10 minutes.
